fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.endpoint

Class ResolverConstructorGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.endpoint.ResolverConstructorGenerator

  • public class ResolverConstructorGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Java source code generator for LighterRequestResolver implementation constructors. This class must generate constructors which which have method references that implement the ResolverFactory functional interface. That is to say that the argument list of the constructor generated by an instance of this class must exactly match the argument list of ResolverFactory.newInstance(InjectionObjectFactory, TypeAdapterFactory).
